#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_raster/raster_properties.rst:545
msgid "Customize raster legend"
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_raster/raster_properties.rst:547
msgid ""
"When applying a color ramp to a raster or a mesh layer, you may want to "
"display a legend showing the classification. By default, QGIS displays a "
"continuous color ramp with min and max values in the :guilabel:`Layers` "
"panel and the layout :ref:`legend item <layout_legend_item>`. This can be"
" customized using the :guilabel:`Legend settings` button in the "
"classification widget."
