#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_raster/raster_properties.rst:1209
msgid "Accessing the raster attribute table"
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_raster/raster_properties.rst:1211
msgid ""
"When opening the :guilabel:`Attribute Tables` for a raster layer that "
"does not have an associated Raster Attribute Table, QGIS displays a "
"notice informing that no attribute table is currently linked to the data "
"source. In this state, the interface provides two options to define and "
"associate a new attribute table:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_raster/raster_properties.rst:1216
msgid ""
