"for an exact values classification (e.g., paletted/unique values): the "
"band name and the applied :guilabel:`Color`. Additional fields of the "
":guilabel:`Red`, :guilabel:`Green`, :guilabel:`Blue` and "
":guilabel:`Opacity` of the color are displayed."
msgstr ""

