msgid ""
"for range values classification (e.g., singleband pseudocolor): the range"
" of values defined by their :guilabel:`Min`,  :guilabel:`Max`, the "
"associated label (:guilabel:`Class`) and color ramp interpolated over the"
" values (:guilabel:`Color`). Additional fields of the minimum and maximum"
" of  :guilabel:`Red`, :guilabel:`Green`, :guilabel:`Blue` and "
":guilabel:`Opacity` of the color ramp are displayed."
msgstr ""

